# Commits

- One goal (`G-xxx`) per commit when possible.
- Message format: `G-xxx: imperative description` (e.g. `G-004: add user auth service`).
- Do not commit unless the user asked, or hooks require it after a successful run.
- Do not combine multiple goals or unrelated file changes.
- Update `docs/07-backlog/goals.md` and `docs/07-backlog/changelog-goals.md` when closing a goal.
